program: WordCoun with Spark Framework in stream Mode


Prerequisites:
=========================================
java JDK +7
spark 1.5.0 Framework
maven +2
kafka
=========================================
create our project with maven tool
=========================================
create project maven:
mvn archetype:generate
 -DgroupId=com.spark.app
 -DartifactId=spark
 -DarchetypeArtifactId=maven-archetype-quickstart
 -DinteractiveMode=false
build our project :
  cd spark
  mvn install
============================================
run our source of streming ... 
in our example we use topic kafka...
============================================
============================================
Steps to run this project
============================================


/home/../spark/bin/spark-submit --class com.spark.App  --master local[2] taget/jar
